(13521, 'Advagraf 5 mg 50 prolonged r. caps. (n/a yet)', 'ادفاجراف 5 مجم 50 كبسولة', '', '5,029', 'Tacrolimus', 'Astellas > egyptian pharmaceutical trading company', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Immunosuppressants', '5 mg', 'Immediate-release formulations of tacrolimus are indicated for the prophylaxis of organ rejection in adult and pediatric patients receiving allogeneic liver, kidney, heart, or lung transplants, in combination with other immunosuppressants.[L8162] Extended-release formulations of tacrolimus are indicated for the prophylaxis of organ rejection in adult and pediatric patients receiving kidney transplants, in combination with other immunosuppressants,[L20034,L41005] and may be used in patients converted from immediate-release formulations.[L41005]
